{"tid":2003971,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/PS4/XBOX]有冇人玩SnowRunner?","createTime":"2020-05-06T06:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T15:27:12.000Z","uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9712944b4fa63db1f4a121d031ac4e92fec36f1a","tid":2003971,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"成日就到目的地先反車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa61a79d0c253ca64d3c3f620b121e8d0c1aef29","tid":2003971,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"冷門自虐貨車驚冇人玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72005f3a37e50966416b18e717442b211a81d3dd","tid":2003971,"uid":28582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"見又插泥又插冰又插沙⋯好爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50339241ea129d5c4a96b3e45d6e7e94c2522ebe","tid":2003971,"uid":278343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"我pc, 有無人開dc一齊玩？"},{"pid":"93fbfb3bf3671eed5dadabaa11831cc742d7a5d1","tid":2003971,"uid":249611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"好似唔錯, 不過個世界好似好死寂咁, 成個世界好似得自己咁"},{"pid":"b7a37ea9849d690ca805818877c8aaf7b0d59309","tid":2003971,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T23:52:22.000Z","msg":"密西根差最後一份合約未做，阿拉斯加北方港口清曬，講下心得<br />\n<br />\n公路軚廢嘅，攞到新車第一時間換走<br />\n泥地最好，要行冰面用加鍊<br />\n泥地&gt;&gt;加鍊/越野&gt;全天候&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;公路<br />\n<br />\n唔用嘅車可以賣，拖卡可以賣，升級都可以賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n善用絞車，快反車時撳快速絞車有機會救到<br />\n偵察車最好裝自動絞車，反咗車著唔到引擎都用到<br />\n<br />\n拖車商店可以當油站用，買載油拖車加滿油之後賣返唔扣錢<br />\n中後期有啲地圖會冇加油站（例如島湖），可以擺定幾個載油拖車喺重要位置以免唔夠油<br />\n<br />\n貨車嚟講黑河車庫門口架艦隊之星初期好有用，升級加高避震同越野軚之後，基本上可以做曬密西根嘅合約<br />\n偵察車黑河市鎮附近可以攞到架Scout 800，升級之後都幾勁<br />\n<br />\n暸望塔開唔曬所有地圖，有啲車同升級會隱藏咗，要仔細留意地圖<br />\n例如德蒙島有架太平洋P16就係"},{"pid":"4422cedde2a7a9a340c994029944619daa70b116","tid":2003971,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T23:55:38.000Z","msg":"呢兩個YouTube channel幾實用<br />\n<br />\n全部升級位置，包括隱藏咗嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBZfRPGRMMPsFhQyXwpVgSw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCBZfRPGRMMPsFhQyXwpVgSw&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=435cdd12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBZfRPGRMMPsFhQyXwpVgSw</a><br />\n<br />\n唔同車軚同車嘅比較<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Sdworld91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FSdworld91&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=c272b005\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/Sdworld91</a>"},{"pid":"22f9291a7bb4497d5166c7ebc428e05429da75d3","tid":2003971,"uid":80473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50339241ea129d5c4a96b3e45d6e7e94c2522ebe","tid":2003971,"uid":278343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"我pc, 有無人開dc一齊玩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:01:23.000Z","msg":"我都係PC，仲未買但係揾緊人一齊玩"},{"pid":"94efc710d88154e8e7833bcdb3744048cf119327","tid":2003971,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T21:19:07.000Z","msg":"就嚟玩完阿拉斯加，手上嘅車越來越勁，感覺挑戰性少咗。攞到ANK MK38之後冇咩地方真係會卡住過唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家直情揸架CAT CT680開圖搵瞭望塔，好過用Scout 800。偵察車升盡條軚都唔夠大，好易卡住"},{"pid":"8975af6f8204ad08eaf963b6c863273d55968dc2","tid":2003971,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:04:53.000Z","msg":"真係有興趣。 之前睇套history channel節目，已經好想試下喺alaska揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bccb5e06fca16741784877ad8eb3c4328a1c74","tid":2003971,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50339241ea129d5c4a96b3e45d6e7e94c2522ebe","tid":2003971,"uid":278343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"我pc, 有無人開dc一齊玩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"有得online打？"},{"pid":"57a0643505d87e2da73aefed6e9b3f8a0301be43","tid":2003971,"uid":36357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"[黃色貨車圈］Snowrunner愛好者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2047183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2047183</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}